_sText:
Thank you for downloading the first map made by CloudVaris, or -|TDD|-Varis =D

Place the map in steam/steamapps/%accountname%/Counter-Strike Source/cstrike/maps

There are 13 spawn points on each side, but lord help you if you max them XD
This map plays best with 4-6 players a team, but if you don't mind chaos, go
ahead and max out those spawn points.

If you would like to report an error, please send an email to cloudstrife240@gmail.com,
or leave a comment on the FPSBanana page for this map.

Take credit for the map, and I will end you.
